# Scope
- Microsoft Graph API v1.0 endpoints for all production code
- Minimal permission scopes following principle of least privilege
- Centralized Graph client in backend/app/services/graph_client.py

# Non-goals
- No Graph /beta endpoints unless absolutely necessary (and behind feature flag)
- No Graph SDK alternatives or custom HTTP clients
- No direct Graph calls from frontend

# Standards
- Prefer v1.0; use /beta only if no v1.0 equivalent (behind flag).
- Minimal scopes; track in docs/PERMISSIONS.md.
